oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Gettysburg Bluegrass Festival (1998)
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Bluegrass music; Festivals; Krauss, Alison, 1971-; Music festivals; Union Station (Musical group);
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: One color window card (blue on white) announcing the 37th Annual Gettysburg Bluegrass Festival with Alison Krauss and Union Station, plus Ralph Stanley and The Clinch Mountain Boys, The Del McCoury Band, The Seldom Scene and others on May 14, 15, 16, and 17. Poster features a metal photoplate of Alison Krauss and Union Station.
